  characterName: Null
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f36fbf6dee429ca41a4cab3318474059, type: 3}
  lines:
  - It is so hard to sleep in this car at night.
  - I hear footsteps around my vehicle all night.
  - Lots of them. I don't know where they even come from.
  - The town is so dead during the day except those two creeps.
  - But I have this feeling that this place is not empty.
  - No, not empty at all.
  - 'I am not a spiritual person but I can''t shake this feeling that the air is
    full of souls. '
  - Suffering.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
